@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Register

actor "User" as User
participant "Form Register" as Form
participant "Sistem" as System
participant "Database (Firebase Auth)" as DB
participant "Halaman Home Aplikasi" as Home

' === Awal ===
User -> Form : Membuka halaman register
activate Form
Form -> User : Menampilkan form register
deactivate Form

' === Input data ===
User -> Form : Input data akun (email, password, nama)
activate Form
Form -> User : Menampilkan data inputan
deactivate Form

User -> Form : Klik tombol Daftar
activate Form

' === Kirim ke sistem ===
Form -> System : Mengirimkan data registrasi
activate System

' === Validasi & simpan ke database ===
System -> DB : Kirim data ke Firebase Auth
activate DB
DB -> DB : Proses pembuatan akun
DB --> System : Akun berhasil dibuat
deactivate DB

' === Konfirmasi hasil ===
System -> Form : Menampilkan pesan "Registrasi berhasil"
activate Form
Form -> User : Menampilkan notifikasi sukses
deactivate Form

' === Arahkan ke Home ===
System -> Home : Menampilkan halaman utama aplikasi
activate Home
Home -> User : Menampilkan menu home
deactivate Home

deactivate System
deactivate Form

@enduml
